<div id="banner">
	<h1>Do you trust Microsoft&#8217;s Trusted Computing Platform?</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>NYTimes: <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2002/06/20/technology/20CODE.html?tntemail1=&amp;pagewanted=print&amp;position=bottom">Fears of Misuse of Encryption System Are Voiced</a></p>

<p>Schoen&#8217;s against it of course. Farber&#8217;s for it: &#8220;It should be capable of supporting a digital rights management regime that can be used to both protect intellectual property and individual privacy and the individual&#8217;s fair use of the intellectual property.&#8221; Farber, you&#8217;re losing whuffie <em>fast</em>, buddy.</p>

